    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in analog performance. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed with surgical precision, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive Double-VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec MacPherson struts and multi-link rear geometry with refreshed bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior free of bolster wear, this vehicle is mechanically and aesthetically indistinguishable from its showroom debut.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
