    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather retains its original scent and supple texture, showing no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle at a significant value. Serious inquiries only for this pristine example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
